       "benefits": "You create a tune so catchy, your foes can't help but dance along.",
       "link": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Feats.aspx?ID=2637",
       "description": "You create a tune so catchy, your foes can't help but dance along. Attempt a  Performance  check against the Will DCs of all enemies in a 30-foot emanation.  The target takes a -10-foot status penalty to its Speed and is  flat-footed , both for 1 round.  The target takes a -5-foot status penalty to its Speed for 1 round.\n  The target is temporarily immune for 1 hour.\n"
