       "link": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Feats.aspx?ID=2799",
       "description": "It's said that the flesh of the right side of a hyena can heal diseases, but that of the left side is poisonous. You can take 1 damage to feed someone blood from your right side and  Administer First Aid  or take 2d8 damage to  Treat Disease  or  Treat Wounds ; in either case, you don't need  healer's tools , and gain a +1 item bonus. Blood from your left side causes the check to critically fail automatically."
