       "link": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Feats.aspx?ID=582",
       "description": "Your debilitations are especially effective on your most powerful attacks. Whenever you critically succeed at an attack roll against an enemy and use Debilitating Strike, add the following debilitation to the list you can choose from.  Debilitation The target attempts a Fortitude save against your class DC with the following effects.  The target is unaffected.  The target is slowed 1 until the end of your next turn.  The target is slowed 2 until the end of your next turn.  The target is paralyzed until the end of your next turn."
