       "benefits": "You've made it almost effortless to combine spells and attacks.",
       "link": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Feats.aspx?ID=2884",
       "description": "You've made it almost effortless to combine spells and attacks. You're permanently  quickened . You can use your extra action only to Strike or to recharge Spellstrike."
